Points at the heels
of her daughter.

00:04:39.822 --> 00:04:41.387
Daughter: "Why not?"

00:04:41.532 --> 00:04:44.165
Mom: "You need to be careful,
you might trip.

00:04:44.297 --> 00:04:46.507
Daughter: "This is part
