00:04:54.243 --> 00:04:58.118
Mom: "Just talk to your boss.
He'll understand your situation."

00:04:58.444 --> 00:05:00.240
Daughter: "It's only been
a month, Mom."

00:05:00.281 --> 00:05:02.213
Mom: "You still need
to be careful."

00:05:02.487 --> 00:05:05.608
"Stay there, I'll get
your flats so you can change."

00:05:05.962 --> 00:05:06.917
Daughter: "Mom,"

00:05:07.001 --> 00:05:08.458
"I'm not ready yet."

00:05:08.521 --> 00:05:09.190
Pause.

00:05:09.981 --> 00:05:11.615
Mom: "What did you say?"

00:05:11.826 --> 00:05:14.538
Daughter: "I don't want to--
